# Proxies for ubi-email-checker — rename this file to "proxies.txt" to use it.
# One per line. Blank lines and #-comments are ignored.
#
# Supported formats:
#   http://user:pass@1.2.3.4:8080
#   https://user:pass@1.2.3.4:8080
#   1.2.3.4:8080            (assumed http://)
#   user:pass@1.2.3.4:8080  (assumed http://)
#
# Proxies are rotated round-robin, and the checker rotates to a fresh one on
# every retry (rate-limits, timeouts, anti-bot). No proxies = direct connection.
#
# Examples (delete these):
# http://user:pass@proxy.example.com:8000
# 203.0.113.10:3128
